---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /about/authors/
title: "Our Authors & Editorial Team – CalcPhi"
description: "Meet the CalcPhi editorial team — CFAs, Chartered Accountants, and CFPs who verify every calculator formula and write our financial guides."
breadcrumbs:
  - name: Home
    url: /
  - name: About
    url: /about/
  - name: Our Authors
---

<main id="main-content">

  <!-- Page header -->
  <div class="authors-page-header">
    <div class="authors-page-header__inner">
      <p class="authors-page-header__eyebrow">Editorial Team</p>
      <h1>Meet Our Financial Experts</h1>
      <p class="authors-page-header__sub">Every calculator and article on CalcPhi is written and independently verified by a qualified financial professional. No rate, formula, or recommendation goes live without sign-off from a credentialed expert.</p>

      <div class="authors-trust-bar">
        <div class="authors-trust-badge">
          <span class="authors-trust-badge__icon">◆</span>
          CFA Institute
        </div>
        <div class="authors-trust-badge">
          <span class="authors-trust-badge__icon">◆</span>
          ICAI Certified CA
        </div>
        <div class="authors-trust-badge">
          <span class="authors-trust-badge__icon">◆</span>
          SEBI-Registered RIA
        </div>
        <div class="authors-trust-badge">
          <span class="authors-trust-badge__icon">◆</span>
          CFP Board
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Author list -->
  <div class="authors-list-wrap">
    <div class="authors-list">

      {% for key, author in authors %}
      <article class="author-row">
        <a href="{{ author.url }}" class="author-row__photo-link">
          <img src="{{ author.image }}"
               alt="{{ author.name }}, {{ author.credentials }}"
               class="author-row__photo"
               width="160" height="160"
               loading="lazy">
          <span class="author-row__cred-badge">{{ author.credentials }}</span>
        </a>

        <div class="author-row__content">
          <div class="author-row__header">
            <div class="author-row__identity">
              <h2><a href="{{ author.url }}">{{ author.name }}</a></h2>
              <p class="author-row__title">{{ author.title }}</p>
            </div>
            <a href="{{ author.url }}" class="author-row__btn">View Profile →</a>
          </div>

          <p class="author-row__bio">{{ author.shortBio }}</p>

          <div class="author-row__footer">
            <div class="author-row__tags">
              {% for skill in author.expertise | slice(0, 4) %}
              <span class="author-row__tag">{{ skill }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            <div class="author-row__articles-count">
              <span>{{ author.articles | length }} article{% if author.articles | length != 1 %}s{% endif %} published</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Editorial pledge -->
  <div class="editorial-pledge">
    <div class="editorial-pledge__inner">
      <div class="editorial-pledge__heading">
        <p class="authors-page-header__eyebrow">Our Standards</p>
        <h2>The CalcPhi Editorial Pledge</h2>
        <p>We hold ourselves to the same standards as regulated financial publications — with every fact sourced, every formula verified, and every rate kept current.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="editorial-pledge__grid">
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">01</span>
          <h3>Credential Verification</h3>
          <p>All authors hold recognised professional qualifications — CFA, CA (ICAI), CFP, or SEBI-RIA registration. Credentials are confirmed before any content is published under their name.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">02</span>
          <h3>Dual Source Verification</h3>
          <p>Every formula and regulatory figure is cross-checked against at least two authoritative sources — CBDT notifications, AMFI data, RBI circulars, PFRDA guidelines, or SEBI publications.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">03</span>
          <h3>Rate Updates Within 7 Days</h3>
          <p>When government rates or tax slabs change, affected pages are updated within 7 days of the official notification. The date of last update is displayed on every calculator page.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">04</span>
          <h3>Editorial Independence</h3>
          <p>No calculator result or written recommendation is influenced by advertising or affiliate relationships. All content is evaluated and approved on accuracy alone — nothing else.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <div class="authors-bottom-cta">
    <div class="authors-bottom-cta__inner">
      <p>Have a correction or found an error in our content?</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="cta-link">Contact the Editorial Team →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>
